SentinelFlight Phase 4 — node decomposition vs. running PX4 SITL (Gazebo Harmonic)
Setup: WSL2 Ubuntu 22.04, ROS 2 Humble, PX4 SITL (gz_x500, headless), Micro
XRCE-DDS Agent bridging PX4 uORB <-> ROS 2 DDS on udp4:8888. Four separate
nodes launched via `ros2 launch sentinel_flight_control mission.launch.py`
instead of Phase 2/3's single in-process node.

